  intro="Flowers have the power to transform any space and any moment. Our floral designers craft arrangements that go beyond the ordinary — from architectural installations that command a room to delicate bouquets that capture a bride's personality in petals."
  features={[
    'Custom bridal bouquets and bridesmaid bouquets',
    'Ceremony floral installations and arches',
    'Reception centerpieces and table garlands',
    'Boutonnieres and corsages',
    'Grand-scale floral installations',
    'Corporate and residential arrangements',
    'Seasonal floral subscriptions',
    'Preserved and dried floral art',
  ]}
  galleryImages={[
    'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520854221256-17451cc331bf?w=900&q=80',
    'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519225421980-715cb0215aed?w=600&q=80',
